    </sec>
    <sec id="Sec4">
      <title>Degenerate strings</title>
      <p id="Par17">We use the concept of a degenerate string to model IUPAC-encoded sequences. A <italic>degenerate symbol</italic>
<inline-formula id="IEq14"><alternatives><tex-math id="M27">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
